basics.name: Ashish Karhade
basics.label: Data Science | Machine Learning
basics.summary: I’m a developer with an interest in Data Science, Machine Learning, Deep Learning and Artificial Intelligence. For over 3 years, I’ve been writing code. I started my development journey as an Android app developer and iOS app developer. I also did Web Development with Flask and Django. I then started Data Science and Machine Learning and now I am in love with it. I am Google Cloud Facilitator and also Developer Students Club core member in the college. We try to make projects to solve problems of small business owners.
